name: URoRRuR'R'R (V)
Lore: 'Leader of a Tusken Raider tribe. Unafraid of machines. Skilled hunter and marksman. Raids moisture farms for water. Roams the Jundland Wastes in search of unwary travelers.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. While with another Tusken Raider: opponent''s weapon destiny draws here are -2; once per turn, may place a card from hand on Force Pile to draw top card of Reserve Deck; and other Tusken Raiders here are forfeit +4.',
